\id JOS Matupi Chin Standard Bible (MCSB) 
\h JOSHUA 
\toc1 JOSHUA 
\toc2 Joshua 
\toc3 Jos 
\mt1 JOSHUA  
\mt2 (Joshua)  
\is1 Joshua Cabu Kawng  
\im \it \+k Joshua\+k* a ti he tah Yahovah-Shua tih Yahovah Tah khangkung Boeipa. Greek ol lamtah (Jesuh) la om.\it* He cabu he Moses a dueknah hnukah Israel ca rhoek mawt hamla a tuek Joshua ming la a khueh. Joshua mawtnah hmuiah Israel ca rhoek loh Kannan ram a lohnah, Israel koca hlainit hamla khohmuen a taelnah kawng a thui. Abraham taengah Pathen loh ol a khueh kawng he olpuei la a tueng sak. Te Boeipa kah kutdoe khohmuen te amih taengla a pha coeng. Israel ca rhoek loh Boeipa taengah huek boe a ngai uh vaengah Kannan khopuei rhoek te a loh uh thai. Jerekho bangla khopuei vongcak pataeng tim. Kannan te Israel kut hmuiah boeih om hlan dae Pathen loh Joshua taengah, “Jordan tuiva khotlak te koca hlainit ham tael pah laeh,” \w a\w* \w ti\w* \w nah\w*. Cabu he Joshua kah olrho phihnah ol neh bawt. Joshua loh pilnam te Pathen taengah uepom la om ham a uen. Olpuei la Shekhem kah a tingtun uh vaengah YHWH Pathen bueng te bawk ham neh, pathen tloe bawk pawt ham paipi a ok uh.  
\iot Sawt Yoeinah  
\io1 Khotlak Kanan a lohnah \ior 1. 1—12. 24\ior*  
\io1 Khohmuen taelnah \ior 13. 1—22. 34\ior*  
\io1 Joshua \ior 23. 1—24. 33\ior*  
\c 1  
\s1 Joshua kah Thalohnah  
\p
